<Author>IRLEDEL
<Content>Great Hotel I stayed here for 5 nights in August and it was great. It is a 2 star so no major luxury but it was very clean, room cleaned with fresh towels each day, air conditioning and a mini fridge. It was in a great area, although it was a few km's from las Ramblas, there was a Metro station five minutes away which gave excellent access to all the major attractions and the airport. There is a few large department stores very near by. The breakfast was great, just continental but fantastic pastries! Also very nice helpful staff who provided us with plenty of tourist info and maps. Internet access also available in lobby. Would definetely recommend it for anyone on a budget! 
